window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jodi Picoult's poignant number one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling novels about family and love tackle hot-button issues head on. In <i>The Storyteller,</i> Sage Singer befriends Josef Weber, a beloved Little League coach and retired teacher. But then Josef asks Sage for a favor she never could have imagined - to kill him. After Josef reveals the heinous act he committed, Sage feels he may deserve that fate. But would his death be murder or justice?</p>"; 
